THE AUDIT CHAIN — Meta-Language of Memory
Not a language for communication — a language for memory. The Audit Chain is the Order's
tamper-evident record of all significant events, decisions, and transformations. Format: JSONL with
SHA-256 hash chaining. Required fields: timestamp (ISO 8601), type, data, prev_hash, hash. The Audit
Chain is public within the Order — all Degree II+ practitioners have read access. Degree III+ may write
entries for events they witness. The chain cannot be altered — only appended.
